text:
Emily Laura Cox (born 14 April 1984 in Ottawa, Canada) is a New Zealand water polo player. She is a member of the New Zealand women's national water polo team. She played at the 2007 World Aquatics Championships 2009 World Aquatics Championships, and 2011 World Aquatics Championships.
She was born in Canada to parents from New Zealand. She played for the University of Hawaii's women's water polo team.
